docstring.long_description: Flojoy Cloud is still in beta, feel free to try it out and give us feedback!
docstring.short_description: Upload a DataContainer to Flojoy Cloud (beta).

parameters.name: default
parameters.description: The data to be uploaded to Flojoy Cloud. Currently only support DataFrame and Boolean.

parameters.name: hardware_device_id
parameters.description: The measurement id of the data to be uploaded to Flojoy Cloud.

parameters.name: test_id
parameters.description: The test id of the data to be uploaded to Flojoy Cloud.(In Flojoy Cloud, right click on the desired test to select its "Copy ID"!)

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: A custom name describing the test.

parameters.name: pass_fail
parameters.description: Optional parameter to define if the test passed or failed.

returns.description: The input DataContainer will be returned as it is.
